('guide-project-supports', 'ca', '<strong>En aquest apartat pots especificar quines altres ajudes, a part de finançament, es necessiten per dur a terme el projecte.</strong><br><br>Poden ser tasques o accions a càrrec d''altres persones (traduccions, gestions, difusió, etc), o bé préstecs específics (de material, transport, maquinari, etc).'),
('guide-project-supports', 'el', '<strong>In this section you will specify what other support, apart from financing, that you will need in order to complete the project.</strong><br><br>They can consist of collaboration or assistance from other people (translations, organization, promotion, etc.) or perhaps specific loans (of material, transportation, hardware, etc.)'),
('guide-project-supports', 'en', '<strong>In this section you will specify what other support, apart from financing, that you will need in order to complete the project.</strong><br><br>They can consist of collaboration or assistance from other people (translations, organization, promotion, etc.) or perhaps specific loans (of material, transportation, hardware, etc.)'),
('guide-project-supports', 'eu', '<strong>Arlo honetan proiektua gauzatzeko, finantzaketaz aparte, zelako laguntza mota behar den zehaztu dezakezu.</strong><br /><br />Lanak beste pertsona batzuek egin ditzakete (itzulketak, kudeaketa, zabalketa, etabar), edo mailegu zehatzak (materiala, garraioa, hardware-a, etabar).'),
('guide-project-supports', 'fr', '<strong> Dans cet espace, précisez les besoins, hors financement, nécessaires à la réalisation de votre projet. </strong><br><br> \r\nCes besoins peuvent prendre la forme de tâches ou d''actions réalisables par d''autres personnes (traduction, gestion, diffusion, etc.), ou de prêts (de matériel informatique, de moyens de transport, etc.)'),
('guide-project-supports', 'it', '<strong>In this section you will specify what other support, apart from financing, that you will need in order to complete the project.</strong><br><br>They can consist of collaboration or assistance from other people (translations, organization, promotion, etc.) or perhaps specific loans (of material, transportation, hardware, etc.)'),
('guide-project-supports', 'pl', '<strong>In this section you will specify what other support, apart from financing, that you will need in order to complete the project.</strong><br><br>They can consist of collaboration or assistance from other people (translations, organization, promotion, etc.) or perhaps specific loans (of material, transportation, hardware, etc.)'),
('guide-project-updates', 'ca', '<b>És molt important que els projectes mantinguin informats els seus cofinançadors i la resta de persones potencialment interessades sobre com avança la seva campanya. Des d''aquest apartat pots publicar missatges d''actualització sobre el projecte, com una espècie de blog públic.</b> A Goteo a més, una vegada s''han aconseguit els fons mínims, per a la segona ronda de cofinançament és crític explicar regularment com ha arrencat la producció, avenços, problemes, etc que permetin la major transparència possible i saber com evoluciona l''inici del projecte, per així tractar de generar més interès i comunitat al seu voltant.'),
('guide-project-updates', 'el', '<b>It''s very important that the projects keep their co-financiers and other potentially interested people up to date about how the campaign is progressing. Use this section like a blog to publish updates about the project.</b>On Goteo, after you''ve achieved the minimum financing, and as you go into the second round, it''s essential to periodically explain how the production, progress, problems, etc. are going in order to allow the most transparency possible in order to generate even more interest and community.'),
('guide-project-updates', 'en', '<b>It''s very important that the projects keep their co-financiers and other potentially interested people up to date about how the campaign is progressing. Use this section like a blog to publish updates about the project.</b>On Goteo, after you''ve achieved the minimum financing, and as you go into the second round, it''s essential to periodically explain how the production, progress, problems, etc. are going in order to allow the most transparency possible in order to generate even more interest and community.'),
('guide-project-updates', 'eu', '<b>Oso garrantzitsua da proiektuak beraien finantzakideak, eta interesaturik egon ahal diren beste pertsonak, informatuta izatea bere kanpaina zelan mugitzen den aurrera. Arlo honetatik proiektuari aurrera pausuei buruzko mezuak idatz dezakezu, blog publikoa antzera.</b> Goteo-n gainera, behin gutxiengo diru kopurua lortu eta gero, 2. finantzaketa txanda hasten denean, garrantzia handia du maiz azaltzeak zelan hasi den produkzio zatia, eman diren aurrera pausuak, egon diren arazoak, etabar. Horrela prozesua ahalik eta garden ikusiko da eta jendea proiektuaren hasieraren jakinaren gainean egongo da, eta interesa eta komunitatea piztuko da honen inguruan.'),
('guide-project-updates', 'fr', '<b>Il est très important que les cofinanceurs et les personnes potentiellement intéressées soient informés régulièrement de l''avancée du projet. Depuis cet espace, vous pouvez publier des messages actualisant votre projet, comme une sorte de blog public.</b> Par ailleurs, dans Goteo, une fois les fonds minimums atteints, le second tour de cofinancement est tout aussi crucial que le premier. Vous devez, dans cette phase de production active, redoubler d''efforts pour communiquer sur l''avancement du projet, sur les éventuels problèmes (la communauté vous soutient à tout moment), et ainsi créer un regain d''intérêt pour la communauté d''une part, mais aussi pour les nouveaux venus et les possibles cofinanceurs, séduits par le déroulement du projet.'),
('guide-project-updates', 'it', '<b>It''s very important that the projects keep their co-financiers and other potentially interested people up to date about how the campaign is progressing. Use this section like a blog to publish updates about the project.</b>On Goteo, after you''ve achieved the minimum financing, and as you go into the second round, it''s essential to periodically explain how the production, progress, problems, etc. are going in order to allow the most transparency possible in order to generate even more interest and community.'),
('guide-project-updates', 'pl', '<b>It''s very important that the projects keep their co-financiers and other potentially interested people up to date about how the campaign is progressing. Use this section like a blog to publish updates about the project.</b>On Goteo, after you''ve achieved the minimum financing, and as you go into the second round, it''s essential to periodically explain how the production, progress, problems, etc. are going in order to allow the most transparency possible in order to generate even more interest and community.'),
('guide-project-user-information', 'ca', '<strong>En aquest apartat has d''introduir les dades per a la informació pública del teu perfil d''usuari. </strong><br><br>Tant si vols presentar un projecte com incorporar-te com a cofinanciador/a, per formar part de la comunitat de Goteo et recomanem que escriguis el teu text de presentació, que afegeixis links rellevants sobre el que fas i pugis una imatge de perfil amb la qual t''identifiquis.'),
('guide-project-user-information', 'el', '    <strong>In this section, you will enter data for the public part of your user profile. </strong><br><br>Whether you want to create a project or co-finance someone else''s, in order to join the Goteo community, we recommend that you carefully edit your presentation text, and include relevant links about what you do as well as a profile image with which you identify.'),
('guide-project-user-information', 'en', '    <strong>In this section, you will enter data for the public part of your user profile. </strong><br><br>Whether you want to create a project or co-finance someone else''s, in order to join the Goteo community, we recommend that you carefully edit your presentation text, and include relevant links about what you do as well as a profile image with which you identify.'),
('guide-project-user-information', 'eu', '<strong>Arlo honetan zure erabiltzaile soslaiko alde publikorako datuak sartuko dituzu. </strong><br><br>Proiektu bat aurkeztu nahi baduzu, edota alde bereko finantzakide bezala parte hartu nahi baduzu, Goteo-ko komunitatean parte hartzeko arreta handiz zure aurkezpen testua idaztea gomendatzen dizugu, baita esteka interesgarriak zuri eta egiten duzunari buruz ipintzea eta parekotzat daukazun irudi bat igotzea.'),
('guide-project-user-information', 'fr', '<strong>Dans cette section, introduisez les informations de votre profil public d''utilisateur</strong><br><br>\r\nQue ce soit pour présenter un projet ou devenir cofinanceur, pour rejoindre la communauté Goteo nous vous recommandons de soigner votre texte de présentation, d''ajouter des liens relatifs à vos activités et d''utiliser une photo de profil qui permette de vous identifier.'),
('guide-project-user-information', 'it', '    <strong>In this section, you will enter data for the public part of your user profile. </strong><br><br>Whether you want to create a project or co-finance someone else''s, in order to join the Goteo community, we recommend that you carefully edit your presentation text, and include relevant links about what you do as well as a profile image with which you identify.'),
