('tooltip-project-cost-required', 'ca', 'Aquest punt és molt important: en cada cost que introdueixis has de marcar si és imprescindible o bé addicional. Tots els costos marcats com a imprescindibles es sumaran donant el valor de l''import de finançament mínim per al projecte. La suma dels costos addicionals, en canvi, es podrà obtenir durant la segona ronda de finançament, després d''haver obtingut els fons imprescindibles.'),
('tooltip-project-cost-required', 'el', 'This section is very important: for each expense that you enter, you have to indicate if it is absolutely necessary or just supplemental. All of the expenses that are marked as necessary will be added to get the full amount of minimum financing required for the project. The sum of the supplemental expenses, in contrast, can be requested during the second round of financing, after having gotten the “necessary” funds.'),
