('tooltip-project-supports', 'fr', 'Sur Goteo, les projets peuvent recevoir d''autres formes d''aides en plus de soutiens financiers. Certaines personnes peuvent ne pas soutenir économiquement les projets mais les aider avec leur talent, temps, énergie etc...'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'it', 'In Goteo, projects can be supported in other ways besides just monetary. There are people who can''t help economically but have plenty to offer in terms of their talent, time, energy, and more.'),
('tooltip-project-supports', 'pl', 'In Goteo, projects can be supported in other ways besides just monetary. There are people who can''t help economically but have plenty to offer in terms of their talent, time, energy, and more.'),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'ca', 'Aquest gràfic mostra la suma de costos imprescindibles (mínims per realitzar el projecte) i la suma de costos secundaris (import òptim) per a les dues rondes de finançament. La primera ronda és de 40 dies, per aconseguir l''import mínim imprescindible. Només si s''aconsegueix aquest volum de finançament es pot optar a la segona ronda, de 40 dies més, per arribar al pressupost òptim. A diferència de la primera, a la segona ronda s''obté tot el que s''ha recaptat.'),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'el', 'This graph shows the sum of essential expenses (the minimum necessary to complete the project) and the sum of secondary expenses (optimal amount) for the two rounds of financing. The first round lasts 40 days, in order to obtain the minimum essential amount. Only those that achieve this level of financing can opt to continue with the second round, for an additional 40 days, in order to achieve the optimal amount of funds. In the second round (in contrast with the first), you get everything you have raised even if you don''t reach the full goal.  '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'en', 'This graph shows the sum of essential expenses (the minimum necessary to complete the project) and the sum of secondary expenses (optimal amount) for the two rounds of financing. The first round lasts 40 days, in order to obtain the minimum essential amount. Only those that achieve this level of financing can opt to continue with the second round, for an additional 40 days, in order to achieve the optimal amount of funds. In the second round (in contrast with the first), you get everything you have raised even if you don''t reach the full goal.  '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'eu', 'Grafiko honek funtsezko gastuak azaltzen ditu (minimoak proiektua aurrera eramateko) eta baita ez funtsezko diren gastuak ere (zenbateko hobezina), finantzazioaren bi txandetan kontutan izateko. Lehenengo txanda 40 egun irauten du, eta funtsezko dirua lortzen saiatzen da. Finantzazio hori lortzen baldin bada, orduan 2. txanda egiteko aukera dago. 40 egun gehiago zenbateko hobezinera heltzeko. Bigarren txanda, lehenengoan ez bezala, jasotako finantzazio guztia jasotzen da (nahiz eta minimoa ez izatea). '),
('tooltip-project-totals', 'fr', 'Ce graphique montre la somme des coûts indispensables (minimum pour réaliser le projet) et la somme des coûts secondaires (budget idéal) pour les deux tours de financement. Le premier tour de 40 jours sert à obtenir le montant minimum indispensable. Une fois ce minimum obtenu, le second tour de 40 jours sera lancé afin d''atteindre le budget idéal. À la différence du premier tour, le second tour permet de toucher le montant collecté quel qu''il soit. ');
