('tooltip-project-totals', 'it', 'This graph shows the sum of essential expenses (the minimum necessary to complete the project) and the sum of secondary expenses (optimal amount) for the two rounds of financing. The first round lasts 40 days, in order to obtain the minimum essential amount. Only those that achieve this level of financing can opt to continue with the second round, for an additional 40 days, in order to achieve the optimal amount of funds. In the second round (in contrast with the first), you get everything you have raised even if you don''t reach the full goal.  '),
